{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji29.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给张维的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给张维的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年9月19日）张维兄："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来信收读，甚以为慰。令堂大人八十寿辰，无以为赠，写了几个字，借致庆贺之忱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺祝健康！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月十九日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]张维，湖南浏阳人，早年同毛泽东有较多交往。当时在上海第二军医大学任教授。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]指毛泽东写的“如日之升，如月之恒”八个字。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":9,"day":19}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":168,"page_end":168},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}